{"tid":610532,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(機會嚟喇飛雲)機戰X陪你度過苦悶的星期五 下午一點開波","createTime":"2018-03-30T04:50:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T14:48:42.000Z","uid":84544,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8514f4f0e2a280df081923d365a9b096cbe330","tid":610532,"uid":84544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-30T04:50:48.000Z","msg":"遊戲簡介:《超級機器人大戰》系列新作《超級機器人大戰 X》的舞台來到異世界，並收錄多款許久未登場的作品像是《聖戰士丹拜因》、《機動戰士鋼彈 F91》以及《無敵鐵金剛凱撒》。另外，《魔神英雄傳》、《BUDDY COMPLEX》、《鋼彈 Reconguista in G》再加上跨越機器人動畫藩籬的《海底兩萬哩》更是首度參戰。嶄新的世界觀再加上一作完結的故事，讓老玩家及新玩家都能迅速上手！ <br />\n<img src=\"http://p2.bahamut.com.tw/M/2KU/88/85d56e4a073e84e38c9ef2eba96zc7o4.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FM%2F2KU%2F88%2F85d56e4a073e84e38c9ef2eba96zc7o4.JPG&h=60441a1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n轉貼by 巴哈姆特<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n直播link:<a href=\"http://www.twitch.tv/iamkwankwan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fiamkwankwan&d=DE904%2F16tISvZ0qSGm9fkDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=59fa1bff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.twitch.tv/iamkwankwan</a><br />\n<br />\nmiss咗直播唔緊要 Youtube 第二日會有backup: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCW2NGImvRg7Oe2uRcphUwhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCW2NGImvRg7Oe2uRcphUwhA&d=DE904%2F16tISvZ0qSGm9fkDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=af51b032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCW2NGImvRg7Oe2uRcphUwhA</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前機戰V嘅直播可以呢到睇番(未完待績)<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TqB7HeTOt7w&amp;list=PLlCyDCCPYvk-SKvpx25nE5EmS6r7_UDxT\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTqB7HeTOt7w%26list%3DPLlCyDCCPYvk-SKvpx25nE5EmS6r7_UDxT&d=DE904%2F16tISvZ0qSGm9fkDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=036772b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TqB7HeTOt7w&amp;list=PLlCyDCCPYvk-SKvpx25nE5E